  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Product Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Product Engineer – Singapore</strong><br />We are seeking a Software Engineer / Product Engineeer with at least 1 year of experience in software development. This is an exciting opportunity to work on modern product development while gaining hands-on exposure to AI-driven technologies, including intelligent chatbots and cloud-based solutions. If you’re passionate about building impactful software and growing your technical expertise in a collaborative environment, this role is for you!<br /><br /><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p><ul><li>Be part of a globally renowned MNC driving digital transformation.</li><li>Unlock excellent career growth opportunities.</li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Work closely with product managers, designers, and other engineering teams to build and enhance product features based on business goals and user requirements.</li><li>Develop and integrate AI-powered capabilities, including conversational chatbots, to improve customer experience.</li><li>Review user feedback, logs, and performance data to continuously improve system quality and usability.</li><li>Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve technical issues discovered during testing or in live environments.</li><li>Create and maintain clear technical specifications and documentation for new and existing features.</li><li>Participate in cloud-based application development, deployment, and maintenance activities.</li><li>Contribute actively within a collaborative team environment, demonstrating strong communication and problem-solving skills.</li></ul><p><strong>An Ideal Candidate:</strong></p><ul><li>Has at least 1 year of hands-on experience in software development or related roles.</li><li>Proficiency in C#, .NET, and SQL Server.</li><li>Experience with cloud platforms such as AWS or Microsoft Azure is an advantage.</li><li>Knowledge of Python, MCP, or Agentic Programming is a plus.</li><li>Familiarity with Natural Language Processing (NLP), Large Language Models (LLMs), or chatbot development is preferred.</li></ul><p>This is a 1 year contract to start, renewable and convertible to permanent.</p>",
